# Per-model artifacts NEVER belong at the parent — they live in models/<m>/logs/.
# A workflow agent that writes/commits these here is a bug (it must work inside its
# submodule). Ignored so stray writes can't pollute model_agent. (logs/process_audit/
# is corpus/program-level and intentionally NOT ignored.)
